 # H2 database
 
+> **Note:** From Play 2.6.x onwards you actually need to include the H2 Dependency on your own. To do this you just need to add the following to your build.sbt:
+>
+> ```
+> libraryDependencies += "com.h2database" % "h2" % "1.4.192"
+> ```
+
